                                n = e.next_in, B = e.input, o = n + (e.avail_in - 5), i = e.next_out, w = e.output, a = i - (t - e.avail_out), r = i + (e.avail_out - 257), s = C.dmax, c = C.wsize, l = C.whave, d = C.wnext, u = C.window, _ = C.hold, h = C.bits, p = C.lencode, m = C.distcode, f = (1 << C.lenbits) - 1, g = (1 << C.distbits) - 1;
                                e: do {
                                    h < 15 && (_ += B[n++] << h, h += 8, _ += B[n++] << h, h += 8), A = p[_ & f];
                                    t: for (;;) {
                                        if (_ >>>= k = A >>> 24, h -= k, 0 == (k = A >>> 16 & 255)) w[i++] = 65535 & A;
                                        else {
                                            if (!(16 & k)) {
                                                if (0 == (64 & k)) {
                                                    A = p[(65535 & A) + (_ & (1 << k) - 1)];
                                                    continue t
                                                }
                                                if (32 & k) {
                                                    C.mode = 12;
                                                    break e
                                                }
                                                e.msg = "invalid literal/length code", C.mode = 30;
                                                break e
                                            }
                                            b = 65535 & A, (k &= 15) && (h < k && (_ += B[n++] << h, h += 8), b += _ & (1 << k) - 1, _ >>>= k, h -= k), h < 15 && (_ += B[n++] << h, h += 8, _ += B[n++] << h, h += 8), A = m[_ & g];
                                            n: for (;;) {
                                                if (_ >>>= k = A >>> 24, h -= k, !(16 & (k = A >>> 16 & 255))) {
                                                    if (0 == (64 & k)) {
                                                        A = m[(65535 & A) + (_ & (1 << k) - 1)];
                                                        continue n
                                                    }
                                                    e.msg = "invalid distance code", C.mode = 30;
                                                    break e
                                                }
                                                if (v = 65535 & A, h < (k &= 15) && (_ += B[n++] << h, (h += 8) < k && (_ += B[n++] << h, h += 8)), (v += _ & (1 << k) - 1) > s) {
                                                    e.msg = "invalid distance too far back", C.mode = 30;
                                                    break e
                                                }
                                                if (_ >>>= k, h -= k, v > (k = i - a)) {
                                                    if ((k = v - k) > l && C.sane) {
                                                        e.msg = "invalid distance too far back", C.mode = 30;
                                                        break e
                                                    }
                                                    if (y = 0, T = u, 0 === d) {
                                                        if (y += c - k, k < b) {
                                                            b -= k;
                                                            do {
                                                                w[i++] = u[y++]
                                                            } while (--k);
                                                            y = i - v, T = w
                                                        }
                                                    } else if (d < k) {
                                                        if (y += c + d - k, (k -= d) < b) {
                                                            b -= k;
                                                            do {
                                                                w[i++] = u[y++]
                                                            } while (--k);
                                                            if (y = 0, d < b) {
                                                                b -= k = d;
                                                                do {
                                                                    w[i++] = u[y++]
                                                                } while (--k);
                                                                y = i - v, T = w
                                                            }
                                                        }
                                                    } else if (y += d - k, k < b) {
                                                        b -= k;
                                                        do {
                                                            w[i++] = u[y++]
                                                        } while (--k);
                                                        y = i - v, T = w
                                                    }
                                                    for (; b > 2;) w[i++] = T[y++], w[i++] = T[y++], w[i++] = T[y++], b -= 3;
                                                    b && (w[i++] = T[y++], b > 1 && (w[i++] = T[y++]))
                                                } else {
                                                    y = i - v;
                                                    do {
                                                        w[i++] = w[y++], w[i++] = w[y++], w[i++] = w[y++], b -= 3
                                                    } while (b > 2);
                                                    b && (w[i++] = w[y++], b > 1 && (w[i++] = w[y++]))
                                                }
                                                break
                                            }
                                        }
                                        break
                                    }
                                } while (n < o && i < r);
                                n -= b = h >> 3, _ &= (1 << (h -= b << 3)) - 1, e.next_in = n, e.next_out = i, e.avail_in = n < o ? o - n + 5 : 5 - (n - o), e.avail_out = i < r ? r - i + 257 : 257 - (i - r), C.hold = _, C.bits = h
                            },
                            it = new Uint16Array([3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 11, 13, 15, 17, 19, 23, 27, 31, 35, 43, 51, 59, 67, 83, 99, 115, 131, 163, 195, 227, 258, 0, 0]),
                            at = new Uint8Array([16, 16, 16, 16, 16, 16, 16, 16, 17, 17, 17, 17, 18, 18, 18, 18, 19, 19, 19, 19, 20, 20, 20, 20, 21, 21, 21, 21, 16, 72, 78]),
                            rt = new Uint16Array([1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 7, 9, 13, 17, 25, 33, 49, 65, 97, 129, 193, 257, 385, 513, 769, 1025, 1537, 2049, 3073, 4097, 6145, 8193, 12289, 16385, 24577, 0, 0]),
                            st = new Uint8Array([16, 16, 16, 16, 17, 17, 18, 18, 19, 19, 20, 20, 21, 21, 22, 22, 23, 23, 24, 24, 25, 25, 26, 26, 27, 27, 28, 28, 29, 29, 64, 64]),
                            ct = function(e, t, n, o, i, a, r, s) {
                                var c, l, d, u, _, h, p, m, f, g = s.bits,
                                    A = 0,
                                    k = 0,
                                    b = 0,
                                    v = 0,
                                    y = 0,
                                    T = 0,
                                    B = 0,
                                    w = 0,
                                    C = 0,
                                    E = 0,
                                    S = null,
                                    x = 0,
                                    I = new Uint16Array(16),
                                    O = new Uint16Array(16),
                                    z = null,
                                    F = 0;
                                for (A = 0; A <= 15; A++) I[A] = 0;
                                for (k = 0; k < o; k++) I[t[n + k]]++;
                                for (y = g, v = 15; v >= 1 && 0 === I[v]; v--);
                                if (y > v && (y = v), 0 === v) return i[a++] = 20971520, i[a++] = 20971520, s.bits = 1, 0;
                                for (b = 1; b < v && 0 === I[b]; b++);
                                for (y < b && (y = b), w = 1, A = 1; A <= 15; A++)
                                    if (w <<= 1, (w -= I[A]) < 0) return -1;
                                if (w > 0 && (0 === e || 1 !== v)) return -1;
                                for (O[1] = 0, A = 1; A < 15; A++) O[A + 1] = O[A] + I[A];
                                for (k = 0; k < o; k++) 0 !== t[n + k] && (r[O[t[n + k]]++] = k);
                                if (0 === e ? (S = z = r, h = 19) : 1 === e ? (S = it, x -= 257, z = at, F -= 257, h = 256) : (S = rt, z = st, h = -1), E = 0, k = 0, A = b, _ = a, T = y, B = 0, d = -1, u = (C = 1 << y) - 1, 1 === e && C > 852 || 2 === e && C > 592) return 1;
                                for (;;) {
                                    p = A - B, r[k] < h ? (m = 0, f = r[k]) : r[k] > h ? (m = z[F + r[k]], f = S[x + r[k]]) : (m = 96, f = 0), c = 1 << A - B, b = l = 1 << T;
                                    do {
                                        i[_ + (E >> B) + (l -= c)] = p << 24 | m << 16 | f | 0
                                    } while (0 !== l);
                                    for (c = 1 << A - 1; E & c;) c >>= 1;
                                    if (0 !== c ? (E &= c - 1, E += c) : E = 0, k++, 0 == --I[A]) {
                                        if (A === v) break;
                                        A = t[n + r[k]]
                                    }
                                    if (A > y && (E & u) !== d) {
                                        for (0 === B && (B = y), _ += b, w = 1 << (T = A - B); T + B < v && !((w -= I[T + B]) <= 0);) T++, w <<= 1;
                                        if (C += 1 << T, 1 === e && C > 852 || 2 === e && C > 592) return 1;
                                        i[d = E & u] = y << 24 | T << 16 | _ - a | 0
                                    }
                                }
                                return 0 !== E && (i[_ + E] = A - B << 24 | 64 << 16 | 0), s.bits = y, 0
                            },
                            lt = U.Z_FINISH,
                            dt = U.Z_BLOCK,
                            ut = U.Z_TREES,
                            _t = U.Z_OK,
                            ht = U.Z_STREAM_END,
                            pt = U.Z_NEED_DICT,
                            mt = U.Z_STREAM_ERROR,
                            ft = U.Z_DATA_ERROR,
                            gt = U.Z_MEM_ERROR,
                            At = U.Z_BUF_ERROR,
                            kt = U.Z_DEFLATED,
                            bt = function(e) {
                                return (e >>> 24 & 255) + (e >>> 8 & 65280) + ((65280 & e) << 8) + ((255 & e) << 24)
                            };

                        function vt() {
                            this.mode = 0, this.last = !1, this.wrap = 0, this.havedict = !1, this.flags = 0, this.dmax = 0, this.check = 0, this.total = 0, this.head = null, this.wbits = 0, this.wsize = 0, this.whave = 0, this.wnext = 0, this.window = null, this.hold = 0, this.bits = 0, this.length = 0, this.offset = 0, this.extra = 0, this.lencode = null, this.distcode = null, this.lenbits = 0, this.distbits = 0, this.ncode = 0, this.nlen = 0, this.ndist = 0, this.have = 0, this.next = null, this.lens = new Uint16Array(320), this.work = new Uint16Array(288), this.lendyn = null, this.distdyn = null, this.sane = 0, this.back = 0, this.was = 0
                        }
                        var yt, Tt, Bt = function(e) {
                                if (!e || !e.state) return mt;
                                var t = e.state;
                                return e.total_in = e.total_out = t.total = 0, e.msg = "", t.wrap && (e.adler = 1 & t.wrap), t.mode = 1, t.last = 0, t.havedict = 0, t.dmax = 32768, t.head = null, t.hold = 0, t.bits = 0, t.lencode = t.lendyn = new Int32Array(852), t.distcode = t.distdyn = new Int32Array(592), t.sane = 1, t.back = -1, _t
                            },
                            wt = function(e) {
                                if (!e || !e.state) return mt;
                                var t = e.state;
                                return t.wsize = 0, t.whave = 0, t.wnext = 0, Bt(e)
                            },
                            Ct = function(e, t) {
                                var n;
                                if (!e || !e.state) return mt;
                                var o = e.state;
                                return t < 0 ? (n = 0, t = -t) : (n = 1 + (t >> 4), t < 48 && (t &= 15)), t && (t < 8 || t > 15) ? mt : (null !== o.window && o.wbits !== t && (o.window = null), o.wrap = n, o.wbits = t, wt(e))
                            },
                            Et = function(e, t) {
                                if (!e) return mt;
                                var n = new vt;
                                e.state = n, n.window = null;
                                var o = Ct(e, t);
                                return o !== _t && (e.state = null), o
                            },
                            St = !0,
                            xt = function(e) {
                                if (St) {
                                    yt = new Int32Array(512), Tt = new Int32Array(32);
                                    for (var t = 0; t < 144;) e.lens[t++] = 8;
                                    for (; t < 256;) e.lens[t++] = 9;
                                    for (; t < 280;) e.lens[t++] = 7;
                                    for (; t < 288;) e.lens[t++] = 8;
                                    for (ct(1, e.lens, 0, 288, yt, 0, e.work, {
                                            bits: 9
                                        }), t = 0; t < 32;) e.lens[t++] = 5;
                                    ct(2, e.lens, 0, 32, Tt, 0, e.work, {
                                        bits: 5
                                    }), St = !1
                                }
                                e.lencode = yt, e.lenbits = 9, e.distcode = Tt, e.distbits = 5
                            },
                            It = function(e, t, n, o) {
                                var i, a = e.state;
                                return null === a.window && (a.wsize = 1 << a.wbits, a.wnext = 0, a.whave = 0, a.window = new Uint8Array(a.wsize)), o >= a.wsize ? (a.window.set(t.subarray(n - a.wsize, n), 0), a.wnext = 0, a.whave = a.wsize) : ((i = a.wsize - a.wnext) > o && (i = o), a.window.set(t.subarray(n - o, n - o + i), a.wnext), (o -= i) ?                             },
                            Ot = {
                                inflateReset: wt,
                                inflateReset2: Ct,
                                inflateResetKeep: Bt,
                                inflateInit: function(e) {
                                    return Et(e, 15)
                                },
                                inflateInit2: Et,
                                inflate: function(e, t) {
                                    var n, o, i, a, r, s, c, l, d, u, _, h, p, m, f, g, A, k, b, v, y, T, B, w, C = 0,
                                        E = new Uint8Array(4),
                                        S = new Uint8Array([16, 17, 18, 0, 8, 7, 9, 6, 10, 5, 11, 4, 12, 3, 13, 2, 14, 1, 15]);
                                    if (!e || !e.state || !e.output || !e.input && 0 !== e.avail_in) return mt;
                                    12 === (n = e.state).mode && (n.mode = 13), r = e.next_out, i = e.output, c = e.avail_out, a = e.next_in, o = e.input, s = e.avail_in, l = n.hold, d = n.bits, u = s, _ = c, T = _t;
                                    e: for (;;) switch (n.mode) {
                                        case 1:
                                            if (0 === n.wrap) {
                                                n.mode = 13;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            for (; d < 16;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            if (2 & n.wrap && 35615 === l) {
                                                n.check = 0, E[0] = 255 & l, E[1] = l >>> 8 & 255, n.check = D(n.check, E, 2, 0), l = 0, d = 0, n.mode = 2;
                                                break

                                            if (n.flags = 0, n.head && (n.head.done = !1), !(1 & n.wrap) || (((255 & l) << 8) + (l >> 8)) % 31) {
                                                e.msg = "incorrect header check", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            if ((15 & l) !== kt) {
                                                e.msg = "unknown compression method", n.mode = 30;
                                                break

                                            if (d -= 4, y = 8 + (15 & (l >>>= 4)), 0 === n.wbits) n.wbits = y;
                                            else if (y > n.wbits) {
                                                e.msg = "invalid window size", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }

                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }

                                                e.msg = "unknown compression method", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            if (57344 & n.flags) {
                                                e.msg = "unknown header flags set", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            n.head && (n.head.text = l >> 8 & 1), 512 & n.flags && (E[0] = 255 & l, E[1] = l >>> 8 & 255, n.check = D(n.check, E, 2, 0)), l = 0, d = 0, n.mode = 3;
                                        case 3:
                                            for (; d < 32;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            n.head && (n.head.time = l), 512 & n.flags && (E[0] = 255 & l, E[1] = l >>> 8 & 255, E[2] = l >>> 16 & 255, E[3] = l >>> 24 & 255, n.check = D(n.check, E, 4, 0)), l = 0, d = 0, n.mode = 4;
                                        case 4:
                                            for (; d < 16;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            n.head && (n.head.xflags = 255 & l, n.head.os = l >> 8), 512 & n.flags && (E[0] = 255 & l, E[1] = l >>> 8 & 255, n.check = D(n.check, E, 2, 0)), l = 0, d = 0, n.mode = 5;
                                        case 5:
                                            if (1024 & n.flags) {
                                                for (; d < 16;) {
                                                    if (0 === s) break e;
                                                    s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                                }
                                                n.length = l, n.head && (n.head.extra_len = l), 512 & n.flags && (E[0] = 255 & l, E[1] = l >>> 8 & 255, n.check = D(n.check, E, 2, 0)), l = 0, d = 0
                                            } else n.head && (n.head.extra = null);
                                            n.mode = 6;
                                        case 6:
                                            if (1024 & n.flags && ((h = n.length) > s && (h = s), h && (n.head && (y = n.head.extra_len - n.length, n.head.extra || (n.head.extra = new Uint8Array(n.head.extra_len)), n.head.extra.set(o.subarray(a, a + h), y)), 512 & n.flags && (n.check = D(n.check, o, h, a)), s -= h, a += h, n.length -= h), n.length)) break e;
                                            n.length = 0, n.mode = 7;
                                        case 7:
                                            if (2048 & n.flags) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                h = 0;
                                                do {
                                                    y = o[a + h++], n.head && y && n.length < 65536 && (n.head.name += String.fromCharCode(y))
                                                } while (y && h < s);
                                                if (512 & n.flags && (n.check = D(n.check, o, h, a)), s -= h, a += h, y) break e
                                            } else n.head && (n.head.name = null);
                                            n.length = 0, n.mode = 8;
                                        case 8:
                                            if (4096 & n.flags) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                h = 0;
                                                do {
                                                    y = o[a + h++], n.head && y && n.length < 65536 && (n.head.comment += String.fromCharCode(y))
                                                } while (y && h < s);
                                                if (512 & n.flags && (n.check = D(n.check, o, h, a)), s -= h, a += h, y) break e
                                            } else n.head && (n.head.comment = null);
                                            n.mode = 9;
                                        case 9:
                                            if (512 & n.flags) {
                                                for (; d < 16;) {
                                                    if (0 === s) break e;
                                                    s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                                }
                                                if (l !== (65535 & n.check)) {
                                                    e.msg = "header crc mismatch", n.mode = 30;
                                                    break
                                                }
                                                l = 0, d = 0
                                            }
                                            n.head && (n.head.hcrc = n.flags >> 9 & 1, n.head.done = !0), e.adler = n.check = 0, n.mode = 12;
                                            break;
                                        case 10:
                                            for (; d < 32;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }

                                        case 11:
                                            if (0 === n.havedict) return e.next_out = r, e.avail_out = c, e.next_in = a, e.avail_in = s, n.hold = l, n.bits = d, pt;
                                            e.adler = n.check = 1, n.mode = 12;
                                        case 12:
                                            if (t === dt || t === ut) break e;
                                        case 13:
                                            if (n.last) {
                                                l >>>= 7 & d, d -= 7 & d, n.mode = 27;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            for (; d < 3;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            switch (n.last = 1 & l, d -= 1, 3 & (l >>>= 1)) {
                                                case 0:
                                                    n.mode = 14;
                                                    break;
                                                case 1:
                                                    if (xt(n), n.mode = 20, t === ut) {
                                                        l >>>= 2, d -= 2;
                                                        break e
                                                    }
                                                    break;
                                                case 2:
                                                    n.mode = 17;
                                                    break;
                                                case 3:
                                                    e.msg = "invalid block type", n.mode = 30
                                            }
                                            l >>>= 2, d -= 2;
                                            break;
                                        case 14:
                                            for (l >>>= 7 & d, d -= 7 & d; d < 32;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            if ((65535 & l) != (l >>> 16 ^ 65535)) {
                                                e.msg = "invalid stored block lengths", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            if (n.length = 65535 & l, l = 0, d = 0, n.mode = 15, t === ut) break e;
                                        case 15:
                                            n.mode = 16;
                                        case 16:
                                            if (h = n.length) {
                                                if (h > s && (h = s), h > c && (h = c), 0 === h) break e;
                                                i.set(o.subarray(a, a + h), r), s -= h, a += h, c -= h, r += h, n.length -= h;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            n.mode = 12;
                                            break;
                                        case 17:
                                            for (; d < 14;) {
                                                if (0 === s) break e;
                                                s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                            }
                                            if (n.nlen = 257 + (31 & l), l >>>= 5, d -= 5, n.ndist = 1 + (31 & l), l >>>= 5, d -= 5, n.ncode = 4 + (15 & l), l >>>= 4, d -= 4, n.nlen > 286 || n.ndist > 30) {
                                                e.msg = "too many length or distance symbols", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            n.have = 0, n.mode = 18;
                                        case 18:
                                            for (; n.have < n.ncode;) {
                                                for (; d < 3;) {
                                                    if (0 === s) break e;
                                                    s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                                }
                                                n.lens[S[n.have++]] = 7 & l, l >>>= 3, d -= 3
                                            }
                                            for (; n.have < 19;) n.lens[S[n.have++]] = 0;
                                            if (n.lencode = n.lendyn, n.lenbits = 7, B = {
                                                    bits: n.lenbits
                                                }, T = ct(0, n.lens, 0, 19, n.lencode, 0, n.work, B), n.lenbits = B.bits, T) {
                                                e.msg = "invalid code lengths set", n.mode = 30;
                                                break
                                            }
                                            n.have = 0, n.mode = 19;
                                        case 19:
                                            for (; n.have < n.nlen + n.ndist;) {
                                                for (; g = (C = n.lencode[l & (1 << n.lenbits) - 1]) >>> 16 & 255, A = 65535 & C, !((f = C >>> 24) <= d);) {
                                                    if (0 === s) break e;
                                                    s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                                }
                                                if (A < 16) l >>>= f, d -= f, n.lens[n.have++] = A;
                                                else {
                                                    if (16 === A) {
                                                        for (w = f + 2; d < w;) {
                                                            if (0 === s) break e;
                                                            s--, l += o[a++] << d, d += 8
                                                        }
                                                        if (l >>>= f, d -= f, 0 === n.have) {
                                                            e.msg = "invalid bit length repeat", n.mode = 30;
                                                            break
                                                        }
